data.name: textBoxDescription.Text
data.value: The program is a tool for: - management of data from the reference standard and power quality analyzers Energomonitor-3.3T, Energomonitor-3.3T1, Energomonitor-3.1K, Energomonitor-3.2, Energotester-PQP, Energotester-PQP-A namely reading/writing measurements results, storing, viewing and processing measurement data on a PC. - forming of reports according to archives stored in the database.
